{"tid":2009911,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英超6隊反對中立場地比賽，希望取消賽季 ，除非取消降班","createTime":"2020-05-10T05:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T08:11:26.000Z","uid":173952,"like":50,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"8a2562a67a64623a7b4d8d85e4d63d8ea367d846","tid":2009911,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T05:54:20.000Z","msg":"為了避免巨大的經濟損失，英超希望能夠重啟今季，計劃在中立場地完成餘下的比賽。不過該計劃遭到了護級區6支球隊的抵制，他們認為失去主場優勢，對球隊的前景不力，他們更希望取消賽季，英超重啟的計劃亦因此受阻。<br />\n<br />\n英超重啟障礙太多<br />\n<br />\n  來自《鏡報》的消息稱，護級區的6支球隊諾域治、屈福特、阿士東維拉、般尼茅夫、韋斯咸和白禮頓已經聯合起來了，他們明確反對在中立場地進行比賽，除非英超取消降班，他們才會讓步。<br />\n<br />\n  其中一間球會的高管表示：「每個人都在為自己的利益而戰，但對於那些面臨降班威脅的球隊來說，犧牲主場優勢是沒有商量餘地的。」<br />\n<br />\n  此外，目前也有不少英超球員隊重啟賽季很牴觸，在仍有感染風險的前提下，球員們不願意冒險複賽。"},{"pid":"55eb88de81bb346242072422ccace835fdae9d91","tid":2009911,"uid":19667,"like":63,"dislike":4,"score":59,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:02:07.000Z","msg":"邊隊六隊呀"},{"pid":"701846715a0a74e331d565ce292a6ad91fd01ec9","tid":2009911,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"55eb88de81bb346242072422ccace835fdae9d91","tid":2009911,"uid":19667,"like":63,"dislike":4,"score":59,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:02:07.000Z","msg":"邊隊六隊呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f6f6604ada9ed3e52ea3cbb2b0ed25eb87ac21","tid":2009911,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"701846715a0a74e331d565ce292a6ad91fd01ec9","tid":2009911,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"55eb88de81bb346242072422ccace835fdae9d91","tid":2009911,"uid":19667,"like":63,"dislike":4,"score":59